Name: Zhu Yuan
Desc: Use it to obtain the Agent or unlock the Agent's Mindscapes.
Desc2:
Snapshots from Zhu Yuan's daily life and from in combat, recording important moments before and after she became an Agent.
These images also provide insights into her fighting style and favorite weapons, helping to better understand her strengths.

There's even a photo of Zhu Yuan when she first joined the Public Security Training Academy? Wow... What a cute little officer!
